# Domain & data

- `core:domain` must not depend on Compose or Android.
- Scoring only in `QuizScorer`; session steps in `QuizEngine`.
- Quiz JSON: `core/data/.../quiz_set.json` via `FakeQuizCatalogSeeder` in `fakeMain` (**dev harness only**). prod は `QuizCatalogRepository` のみ（`getDefaultQuizSet` なし）。
- Runtime: `quiz.runtime` (`fake` | `prod` | `local`) adds `src/fakeMain` or `src/prodMain` to `commonMain` via `kotlin.srcDir` + Metro graph (`FakeQuizAppGraph` / `ProdQuizAppGraph`). `local` uses `prodMain` + Firebase Emulator. Resolved in `gradle/quiz-runtime.gradle.kts` (`-Pquiz.runtime`, Android task `assembleFakeDebug` / `assembleProdDebug` / `assembleLocalDebug`, default `fake`). Android app: productFlavor `runtime` (`fake` / `prod` / `local`).
- **prod**: quiz + ranking from remote cloud; network required — no silent fallback to fake/JSON.
- **local**: same as prod but connects to Firebase Emulator Suite (`FirebaseEmulatorConnector`).
- **fake**: bundled JSON + in-memory ranking for local dev/tests only.
- Repositories: interface in domain; fake/prod impls in matching source set; wire via Metro `@ContributesBinding` + `AppDependencies.init(graph)`.
- “Today” filtering: `InstantProvider` + `isSameDay` — never hardcode dates in UI.
- Extend `Question` sealed types in domain; map JSON in `QuestionDto.toDomain()`.
- AGP 9: KMP modules use `androidKmpLibrary` + `kotlin.androidLibrary {}`; never combine `kotlinMultiplatform` with `com.android.library` in the same module.
